asset.author: Volcom
asset.hookText:
With close to 200 competitors and it being the last CA qualifier, we knew we were in for a show. And what better venue? The Bear Mountain base area of course. As always, Bear went above and beyond with the set-up. A big thank you goes out to Clayton Shoemaker, Greg Seabre, and Dan Neilson for putting together a super fun jam site. The snow park is in full swing! Go get it if you haven't been.  See photos and read the whole story at:  http://vol.cm/xE9SJk
